abstract: Would the Jaguars dare part with running back Maurice-Jones Drew? Maybe, if the price is right.
snippet: Would the Jaguars dare part with running back Maurice-Jones Drew? Maybe, if the price is right.
lead_paragraph: With the N.F.L.'s trade deadline approaching (Oct. 18) and the Jets in need of a jolt, should they be among the teams looking to buy? If so, Jacksonville could be a place to look.
